{
  "texts": [
    "According to our topic outline in Appendix B), 255k instructions are generated, with corresponding answers generated with GPT-4.",
    "Math and code data.",
    "The computational music community lacks symbolic music datasets, and we hypothesize that including math (Cobbe et al., 2021; Kenney, 2023; Yue et al., 2023; Li et al., 2023) and code (Li et al., 2023; Wang et al., 2023a) may enhance the reasoning power of symbolic music.",
    "Empirically, we find this helps to improve the performance of music LLMs.",
    "Except for the general corpora, all the other datasets were constructed as conversation forms for one or more rounds."
  ]
}